OOC: Out of curiousity, what does bicephalous mean?

BIC:
Sinnertwins prey had almost stopped moving, he almost was depressed, he
stopped breathing flames on Condor, and started to tear into the robot with
his teeth and claws, savagely riping what he could, "Stupid Autobot, they
not last long" said one voice in between bites, the other concured, "It not
smart to insult Terrorcons, or to run from them".
